{
  "chapter": 28,
  "chapter_summary": "第28回\"生死之间\"，胡铁花与琵琶公主在沙漠中濒死，互诉衷肠。琵琶公主透露自己的身子已交给楚留香（老臭虫），胡铁花虽痛苦却仍理解。两人发现受伤的鹰，靠吃鹰肉恢复体力。随后发现石驼（皇甫高）与王冲（柳别飞）被石观音的黑衣属下围攻，胡铁花出手相救。柳别飞揭示石驼就是华山七剑之首皇甫高，被石观音害得身残，华山派基业也因此断送。琵琶公主对华山派的衰落冷言相讽。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"我们这一辈子，只怕休想找得到那老臭虫了。\"",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"我们本不该走这条路的。\"",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"不错，我们本不该走这条路的，但这难道怪我?你不是说，在沙漠上比我有用得多么?为什么也跟我一样，狗也似的躺在这里没法子?\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"我实在不该跟你来，拖累了你，否则你那袋水若是一个人喝，至少也还可以多支持一阵子。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"我真是个混账，这种事怎能怪你?我一个大男人，连一个女孩子都保护不了，居然还有脸在这里发脾气。\"",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"这不怪你，怪我……我现在只想死，最好马上就死。\"",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"咱们就算不想死，只怕也没法子活下去了。\"",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"我居然会和你死在一起，这只怕是谁也想不到的事吧?\"",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"能和你死在一起，倒是件令人愉快的事，你……你实在是个非常美丽的女孩子，你……你……\"",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"但我们死也该死得快乐些，是么?\"",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"你……你可是要我……\"",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"我要你……我真的要你，除了你之外，我不知还要什么?\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"你……你为什么这样……为什么这样?难道你不愿意?\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"我……我是愿意的，在临死之前，我已决定将什么都交给你，但我却不能不告诉你一件事。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"什么事?\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"我的……我的身子已不再完整，已交给别人了。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"谁?\"",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"就是他。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"我也想要你的，我实在也已没法子控制自己，只想忘记一切，死在你怀里，但……但也不知为了什么，我竟无法将这件事瞒住你。\"",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"不要说了……不要说了……\"",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"老臭虫。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"你现在很恨他么?\"",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"哼!\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"你认为我们和他在一起，实在太吃亏了，是不是?\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"嗯!\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"但我们却都是心甘情愿和他在一起的，他并没有强迫过我们，是不是?\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"嗯!\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"说来说去，我们两个倒真是同病相怜，虽然很恨他，却又忍不住要喜欢他。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"有时，我也不知道这是为了什么?\"",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"因为老臭虫的确是值得别人喜欢的，是不是?\"",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"你真不愧是他的好朋友……\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"瞧什么?我的头难道忽然变成两个?\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"这鹰是从哪里来的?又怎会受了伤?莫非附近有人来了?\"",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"好快的剑法。\"",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"是不是他?\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"绝不是，若是他出的手，这鹰绝对没法子还能飞这么远，何况，就算是只扁毛畜牲，他也舍不得杀死。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"那么，会不会是你另外那个朋友?\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"也不是，姬冰雁从来不用剑的。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"无论如何，这两只鹰来的倒很是时候。\"",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"把它吃下去。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"吃下去?这怎么吃得下去?\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"你假如不想死，就一定要想法子吃下去，能吃多少就多少，尽量多吃，越多越好，知道么?\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"你这样子吃法，永远也恢复不了力气的，要像我这样吃，你看……\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"我……我不能这样吃，我吃不下去。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"你只要闭起眼睛，幻想着自己吃的是白切羊肉酱加烧饼，你就吃得下去了。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"你在这里等着，我过去瞧瞧。\"",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"我也要去。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"好，来吧……看来除了那老臭虫外，也没有别人能管得住你……但你可千万小心些才好。\"",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"你瞧，那……那不是你们的马夫么?\"",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"这一次，你一定要在这里等着。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"但若有人逃到我这边来，我总不能看着不出手吧?\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"胡某也不愿多伤无辜，只要放下刀来，绝不伤你们性命。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_chong",
      "speaker_name": "王冲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"这些人神智已狂，完全不可理喻，只有杀了他们，别无他法。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"你这是何苦?\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"咱们龟兹国里若有这么多勇士，咱们又何致像今天这么惨。\"",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"大恩不敢言谢，今日若非胡大侠仗义相助，我兄弟真是死无葬身之地了。\"",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"你们是兄弟?\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_chong",
      "speaker_name": "王冲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"虽非骨肉，情同手足。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"如此说来，你们是早已认识的?\"",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_chong",
      "speaker_name": "王冲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"在下浪迹天涯，为的就是要寻找他，说来……这已快二十年了。\"",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"二十年来，江湖中已不复能见到正宗华山剑法，阁下方才那一招'惊虹贯日'，当真已可算是武林绝响。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_chong",
      "speaker_name": "王冲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"胡大侠过奖了。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"据在下所知，纵然在昔年华山剑派全盛时，能将这一招'惊虹贯日'使得如此精妙，也不过只有寥寥数人而已，而华山高手剑客中，却绝没有'王冲'这个人的，阁下现在总该将真实姓名说出来了吧?\"",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_chong",
      "speaker_name": "王冲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"在下只不过是江湖中的一个无名小卒而已，阁下又何必……\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"到了现在，阁下还不肯以真面目示人么?要知道一个人的姓名虽能瞒得住人，但剑法却是瞒不住人的。\"",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_chong",
      "speaker_name": "王冲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"在下性命蒙胡大侠所救，实也不敢再以虚言相欺。\"",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_chong",
      "speaker_name": "王冲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"实不相瞒，在下本姓柳，小名别飞……\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"柳别飞，莫非就是昔年华山派掌门真人的收山弟子，华山七剑外，最负盛名的'神龙小剑客'么?\"",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "speaker_name": "柳别飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"岁月催人，昔日的小伙子，如今两鬓也已斑白了。\"",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"阁下既是柳大侠，他……\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "speaker_name": "柳别飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"他就是我的大师兄皇甫高。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"难道竟是'华山七剑'之首，侠义之名，传遍八州，天下武林中人莫不敬仰的'仁义剑客'?\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "speaker_name": "柳别飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"正是。\"",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"石驼\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"那石观音究竟和皇甫高大侠有什么仇恨?要害得他如此惨?\"",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "speaker_name": "柳别飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"此中曲折，说来话长，非但皇甫大哥被她害得身成残废，我华山派数百年的基业，也就是断送在这……这恶魔手里的。\"",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"现在，你总算已找着他了，你又想怎么样呢?\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "speaker_name": "柳别飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"我……我……\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"你难道不想报仇?\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "speaker_name": "柳别飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"报仇……报仇……\"",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"你可知道我皇甫大哥为何自甘沦落，与驼马为伍?\"",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"我也早已看出，他必有难言的隐痛。\"",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "speaker_name": "柳别飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"他隐姓埋名，忍辱负重，为的就是不愿复仇。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"为什么?\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "speaker_name": "柳别飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"只因他知道以我们之力要想复仇，实无异以卵击石，他不愿我华山一脉就此断送，也不忍令华山弟子全都死尽死绝。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"华山弟子，现在难道还有活着的么?\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "speaker_name": "柳别飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"所存实也无几了。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"哦!原来还有几个，我却以为早已死光了。\"",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "speaker_name": "柳别飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"你……\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"昔年'华山七剑'纵横江湖，是何等的光彩，江湖中人提起'华山派'三个字，谁敢不退避三分，就连我这化外之民，也已久慕华山风采，但现在……\"",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"但现在江湖中人却已几乎忘记武林中有过\"",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    }
  ],
